page.content: Last lesson today is Maths. After Maths I go and wait for the bus. I ride on the bus to the village of Wembury and go and help look after a friends' children. I help until 6.00 pm. when my dad comes and picks me up. When I get home I do my Maths homework, then I do my{clarinet practice. If there is time after my tea I watch some{television.}Then it is time to get ready for bed. I go to bed at about 9.30 pm. This is a typical Wednesday for me. Sarah Parfitt. Of the 71 first year pupils interviewed,20 said that they went to {bed}at the same{time}as Sarah.The most popular time ,however,was 10 pm with only a few boys staying up later.Five did not go to bed until half past eleven.
